Class ReliableInOrderMsgLayer

java.lang.Object
  ReliableInOrderMsgLayer

public class ReliableInOrderMsgLayer
extends java.lang.Object

Layer above the basic messaging layer that provides reliable, in-order delivery in the absence of faults. This layer does not provide much more than the above. At a minimum, the student should extend/modify this layer to provide reliable, in-order message delivery, even in the presence of node failures.
